Package com.example.eventscan.Helpers

Class QRAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventscan.Helpers.QRAnalyzer
public class QRAnalyzer extends Object
This class handles the opening of the camera, as well as scanning the QR Code and retrieving the relevant information from it. Will be consolidated with QR Codec in the future.
